snippet.textDisplay: That was such a weird trailer. For one, where the heck was was my deafening intro soundtrack, I was all prepared when the "Long Time Ago" Title came up, but nothing happened. Then all that was shown was things we already knew: just Lego-affied clips. I think what we really need from Lego Games now is new or updated gameplay, because the story doesn't quite have enough. But actually, the trailer has me kinda confident that there will be some new stuff in this game because of BB-8 slapping in that power tile thing.
